data.title: University of Illinois College of Medicine
data.text:
Dr. Robert Huibonhoa is originally from the Philippines. He earned his medical degree from University of the East/Ramon Magsaysay Memorial Medical Center College of Medicine. He completed his pediatric residency in the United States at New York Medical College/Metropolitan Hospital Center. Robert has a passion for education and enjoys sharing what heâ€™s learned along his journey with others.

Outside of work, Robert enjoys documentary and film photography, film making, visual arts, art, and literature.
